     This package computes the intersection of various lines  and
     planes.  The following intersection structure is returned:

     typedef struct {
       int type;
       Point p;
       Vector v;
       Normal n;
     } Intersection;

     Type will be one of I_EMPTY, I_POINT, I_LINE, or I_PLANE.  A
     line  is  desribed by a point and a vector; a plane is given
     by a point and a normal.


