     NNNNoooorrrrmmmmaaaallll nnnn3333;;;;

     Intersect three planes.  Depending on how the code  is  com-
     piled,  the true intersection will be calculated (and may be
     a point, a line, a plane, or  empty)  or  a  best  point  of
     "intersection"  will  be calculated (in the case of multiple
     solutions, one is choosen; if no  solutions,  then  a  point
     near p1,p2, and p3 is choosen).



